📊 Product Sales Dashboard (Power BI)
🧠 Project Overview
This dashboard provides a detailed analysis of product sales performance, helping to identify top-performing products, salespersons, and regions.
It was built using Power BI for interactive data visualization and analysis.

🧩 Key Insights
💼 Top Salespersons: Identified high performers contributing to overall revenue.
📦 Product Performance: Compared total sales by product category.
🌎 Regional Sales: Visualized contribution of each region to total sales.
📈 Trend Analysis: Tracked total sales over time to monitor growth.
⚙️ Tools Used
Microsoft Power BI
Excel / CSV dataset (source)
Data cleaning & transformation using Power Query
📸 Dashboard Preview
Product Sales Dashboard

🚀 How to Use
Download the .pbix file from this repository.
Open it in Power BI Desktop.
Explore interactive visuals and filters.
